  <brief_title>TaxoteRe Plus Cisplatin Versus AlImta Plus Cisplatin in 1st Line Non-squamous Cell Type Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>TRAIL</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase III Study of TaxoteRe Plus Cisplatin Versus AlImta Plus Cisplatin in 1st Line Non-squamous Cell Type Lung Cancer</official_title>
