  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is:

        -  A multicenter, prospective, randomized, phase 3 trial.

        -  To prove non-inferiority of Taxotere/Cisplatin compared to Pemetrexed/Cisplatin as a
           front line treatment of patients with non-squamous cell lung cancer.

        -  276 patients will be recruited.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Docetaxel is being used in 60mg/m2 3 weekly dosage in Japan and several east Asian
      institutions. Docetaxel 60mg/m2 and Cisplatin 70 mg/m3 3 weekly regimen will be compared to
      Pemetrexed 500mg/m2 and Cisplatin 70 mg/m2 3 weekly regimen in first line NSCLC with
      non-squamous histology.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
